00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:36,200
Give me some financial aid, donate to the arts.

396
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:49,800
Do you know what WeChat message Teacher Jia Yin sent to me?

397
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:53,200
She said she already helped you make an appointment to see the eye specialist tomorrow afternoon.

398
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:56,000
