00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:28,900
That's because you didn't see how he rejects people.

410
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:31,500
He's really too cruel.

411
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,800
"I don't mean anything by it,

412
00:29:34,800 --> 00:29:38,500
