00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:06,400
What about... we just forget about it?

420
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:08,000
Forget about it?!

421
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:10,110
Xia Miaomiao, when you go to the art club for the afternoon meeting,

